```

**Key parameters:**
- `--frames N`: Export N frames (outputs `xxx_f0.bmp ... xxx_fN.bmp`)
- `--frame-ms MS`: Sleep MS milliseconds between frames
- `--no-update`: Skip `dong_view_update()` calls (isolates rendering-only issues)

